<P>BY HUGH DOWNMAN, M.D.</P>
<P>EDINBURGH: PRINTED FOR J. BELL AND J. BRADFUTE; G. G. J. &amp; J. ROBINSON; G. &amp; T. WILKIE, AND G. KEARSLEY, LONDON. M,DCC,XC.</P>
